HCI Capital Cancels Beluga Shipping Contracts, FTD Reports

-- B y   A l l i s o n   C o n n o l l y
-- 
2011-03-16T07:15:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-16/hci-capital-cancels-beluga-shipping-contracts-ftd-reports.html
Shop financier  HCI Capital AG (HXCI)  has
canceled all contracts with Bremen, Germany-based shipping
company Beluga Shipping GmbH following fraud allegations,
 Financial Times Deutschland reported  today, citing an
unidentified spokeswoman for HCI.  HCI Capital has transferred 20 ship contracts to Hamburg,
Germany-based HCI Hammonia Shipping AG, the newspaper quoted her
as saying in an interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Allison Connolly in  Frankfurt  at 
 aconnolly4@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Phil Serafino at   pserafino@bloomberg.net . 